Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand it in my head,\Nbut why can't I move?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I say I have no reason to win,\Nbut why is it so painful when I lose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's always a half-measure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...with everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.52,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Child of God (Part Three) Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Stare
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's staring at me.\NHe's totally staring at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's huge... I'm scared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I'm Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rei. Rei Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so. You became\Na professional shogi player in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nice to meet you. I'm Yuusuke Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I play baseball and hope to become\Na professional in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure if I should rely on\Na baseball referral to enter a local high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or go to a rural school that has a chance at\Nentering the national high school championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, my dad told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this world, there are kids like this{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who decided his own path in middle school\Nand then became a professional.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you want to become a professional, you need\Nto be courageous and make a decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to go to a high school in Shikoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A coach who helped me at a junior tournament\Ninvited me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kiriyama, after becoming a professional,\Nyou went back to high school a year later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looking at his serious expression,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was a question that needed more than\Na superficial answer. It needed sincere words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realized that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...what should I convey to him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really only specialize in shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really good at socializing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like studying, but I couldn't fit in at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret deciding on the direction\Nof my life so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I wanted memories\Nof not running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}N-Now I'm getting embarrassed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I giving such a speech?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}He's a middle school student\Nwhom I just met.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Blush
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only I will know my own memories\Nof "running away" and "slacking off".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at critical moments, my coach\Noften tells me to "believe in myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you have even one memory\Nof "running away" or "slacking off,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you'd think,\N"But I slacked off that time after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So... I can't explain it well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you wanted\Nto get rid of things like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It got through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm really happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It felt like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...if I let my guard down,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tears would stream down my face,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I panicked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how happy I was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry we're late. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Right. Oh, but I wanted to talk a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if you don't mind, let's talk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can get in touch with me\Nthrough Hina... I mean Ms. Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it. I'll call you soon, Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shrivel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you, Hina!\N- Thank you, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind of a cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? He's really got his act together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you two talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pshnore... Pshnore... Ps...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can see time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I made salted rice balls\Nout of all the rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's also tempura, a boiled egg,\Npickled vegetables...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}That night, the warm dinner\Nand the various events of the day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}made my stomach feel fluffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't fall sleep easily...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so I stayed up late solving shogi problems.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suddenly, the smell of the water\Nand the sound of the waves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}climbed up to my room on the sixth floor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to ask you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like how he asked me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If a day comes\Nwhen I'm able to ask someone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The scenery reflected in those eyes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}The stories that exist\Non the other side of the storm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I still don't know the stories\Nthat are told on the other side of the goal.{\i0}
