Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Maybe we should have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, Hina is extremely nervous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Normally she's energetic like a ball of light,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or get dejected like a dark cloud,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or angry like a bolt of lightning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's lively, in more ways than one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think of it as\Na good characteristic of hers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she's as stiff as a board.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that's because in front of her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takahashi is right there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Nervous\NNervous
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's been a while since I've come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since second grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's have curry already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ughhh
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Ahhhh
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come on, Hina. Get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is this enough rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Do you think curry will be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Maybe a fancier dinner would've been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Curry is too ordinary.\NIt won't make him happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It'll be fine. It came out really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Received Messages\NFrom: Takahashi\NTitle: It's Takahashi.\NMr. Kiriyama, are you free on Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a8}1 New Message
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a message from Takahashi,\Nasking if I'm free on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can we both go to your house, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuhpoof
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:16.38,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel kind of bad now, to get her so nervous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rei, Momo is hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Why aren't you\Ngoing to be home Saturday night, Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to eat dinner with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was suddenly asked\Nto work at the store on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you make curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can make it in advance and just warm it up\Nwhen he gets here. Easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No worries about messing up either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's too ordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be, let's see,\Nfancier and more elaborate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't learned your lesson at all,\Nhave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten about the bento already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, when it comes to making dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ping!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}What? Dinner? Did you just say dinner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}- Right, right?\N- Yeah Senpai, I totally heard it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! The "dinner" I'm talking about\Nisn't your "dinner"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just said it twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dinner? Dinner?\NSis, are you making our dinner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snack
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Looks like she lost
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Meow\NNom Nom\NMeroweow\NDelicious\NCrunch Crunch\NMrawrawr
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay, then how about deep-fried chicken\Nas a topping bonus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Curry\N(Tasty)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Deep-fried Chicken\N(Tasty)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deep-fried...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Super\NTasty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what would you say to adding\Na hot spring egg on top of that? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Super Tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:38.25,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hohohohoho
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A hot spring egg, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mega Tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like that's settled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:40.76,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phew
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as for Takahashi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hot spring egg on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Thump\NThump\NGot effected by it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thump Thump Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thump Thump Thump Thump Thump Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's eating it in such a delicious way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kawamoto, your curry is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The deep-fried chicken topping alone is great,\Nbut then hot spring egg, too? Pretty fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like at a restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You can have seconds, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes! Thank you, Sis!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask Mr. Kiriyama something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Kawamoto, can I borrow your VCR?\N- S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,57th NHK Cup (7)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Crisp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}- That's the guy who came over last time!\N- B-Bodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What? Nikaidou 4th-Dan has been here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I-Incredible? He's a person on TV?\NHe never said anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, I see. He's your best friend,\Nright, Mr. Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Best friend? H-How did it get to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two are close, huh? Mr. Nikaidou\Noften says that, in interviews and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a second. If Nikaidou is commentating...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we save this video\Nfor next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black, 6-f-Gold General.\NWhite, 3-d-Bishop+.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black, 6-d-Dragon Horse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama 5th-Dan, has seven minutes left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thank you for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-Rei! Why are you on TV?\NYou said you're in a shogi club, at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}- Rei, no run away!\N- Momo, you're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh shoot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap. I didn't know Mr. Kiriyama\Nwas keeping it a secret.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, kid? Your secret's been disclosed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Thank you for letting me come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takahashi's kid. You've gotten big!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's your old man and granddad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're both well, sir. They were playing shogi\Nand fighting over it again last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they wanted me to ask\NKiriyama 5th-Dan a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The NHK Cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which part? I was watching it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Black, 4-b-Dragon Horse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}What? What are you doing, Kiriyama?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I don't know if he went in\Nfor the kill or to be killed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Nikaidou 4th-Dan? Nikaidou 4th-Dan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's some passionate commentary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and grandpa said\Nthey didn't think that was the losing move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They wondered what\NNikaidou 4th-Dan was going on about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Same, King, Black. 5-e-Gold General.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's right. That was the losing move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seems like he lost
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad and Grandpa\Ndidn't think the move was that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, they said it felt\Nlike an aggressive move with manly spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After my opponent surrounded me, he waited\Nfor me to make a mistake, and didn't attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought,\N"All right, let's see if this is a mistake or not."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't try to act cool, Kiriyama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}NHK Cup Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you really want to win, then persevere!\NDon't just attack, you have to defend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've been acting a little weird lately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Nikaidou, we can't see the board!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You used to be more careful and single-minded\Nback in the 3rd Dan league!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bravery and recklessness\Nare similar but different!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama, can you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Nikaidou 4th-Dan,\Nyou're too close to the camera!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take better care of your shogi,\Nand yourself, Kiriyama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're way too close! Nikaidou 4th-Dan,\Nthey're playing on the 4th floor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He can't hear you! Please calm down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got yourself a good friend there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm saying this as your best friend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your best friend, he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, youth! I'm jealous, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bodoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen! I'm only going to say this once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's kind of important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, Kiriyama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, get this on video\Nso you can watch it over and over again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Wow, that's amazing.\N- They're BFF's after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take better care of yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're not doing that,\Nis the reason why you can't progress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Explode
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The kid's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, what he's saying is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"I'm only going to say this once!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm only going to say this once!"\N"So record it and watch it over and over again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}"So record it and watch it\Nover and over again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good point! But I think Mr. Nikaidou's\Nfeelings for you as his best friend are genuine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wheee-ooo, you guys are sweet and sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's hope for this generation yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Haaaa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time\NI've heard you raise your voice, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her words...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...surprised me a little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all,\Nnobody had ever said that to me before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rei.\NWould you please teach me how to play shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.00,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Important Things. Important Matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:56.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teach Me How to Play Shogi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would you teach me how to play shogi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had no idea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If someone had interest in a world I was in,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know it would make my stomach\Nfeel fluffy, and happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...\NFirst, what kind of board should we go with?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A plastic mat would probably be better\Nthan a wooden board.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it'll be used\Non the tea table in the living room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}And maybe we should use these plastic pieces,\Nso they can handle it easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Besides, Momo often spills milk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ahhh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Splash
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Momo's milk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Momo's milk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Water of life, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Zoom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The characters aren't in cursive,\Nso it's easy to read.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And maybe we should have an\Nillustrated guide, so it's easier to understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, which one would be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:20:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend Taniyama and Senzaki\Nfor beginners, since they're easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikaidou?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shucks. They're sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um... I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thrilled, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:14.88,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Passionate\NGood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sense the importance\Nof spreading the word, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}If it's okay with you, can I help?\NYou don't have to,\Nbut if you really wanted,\NI could totally help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Sparkle\NSparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Sparkle\NSparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, who are you going to teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Sparkle\NSparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Sparkle\NSparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Looks like he lost from the pressure,\Npassion, and many other things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Yeay, Bododo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No problem. The pleasure is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:26.64,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Baaam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it'll be okay.\NI hope I can remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't worry! It looks difficult,\Nbut it's surprisingly simple to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.77,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bododo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you do feel that it's difficult,\NHina, it won't be your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:44.53,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bododo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The person who's teaching you\Nis fully responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,good luck, Mr. Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Slap
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's my turn after a lead-in like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.04,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll give you a simple explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On top of this board with nine rows\Nand nine columns, you and your opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,both use 20 pieces with eight different types.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During the game, you take pieces\Nand your pieces are taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the main point is to capture\Nyour opponent's king.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The person who goes first is black,\Nthe second person is white,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then you go back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Each of the eight different types of pieces\Nhas its own attributes and range of movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, the columns are called "files"\Nand the rows are called "ranks."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First Player
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Second Player
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rows are marked with numerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And all of the boxes have an address.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next, about the movement\Nof each kind of piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Pull
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's stiff! You're too stiff, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Write\NWrite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um Um
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her expression says,\N"Mmm, maybe this is difficult after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Black goes first...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Hina, Momo would like some yogurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be so nervous, it'll all go in\None ear and out the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}White goes second...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have to make the first impression\Neasily understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Hina and Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Drawn and Written by\NHarunobu Nikaidou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shogi for Beginners Picture Book
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's look at this picture book together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Shiny
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ha-Meow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There's a king, too.\NAll different kinds of kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shogi is a game in which you use\Neight different types of personality and pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}like this to capture your opponent's king.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You play on this board of 81 squares,\N9 rows and 9 columns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The three rows of pieces\Nin front of you is your land.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.48,0:22:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Your Army
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The three rows on the other side\Nare from your opponent's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Enemy Army
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next I'll introduce\Nthe personalities of each type of cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:43.82,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:43.82,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:43.82,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes! Good responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.49,0:22:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nikaidou... You're amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this feeling I have?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:55.96,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer: Exclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:58.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teach Me How to Play Shogi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:35.31,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 8
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.55,0:24:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Really?! That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.93,0:24:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.35,0:24:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It came out wonderfully, Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.06,0:24:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikaidou! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.36,0:24:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... I'm going to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver you my meaty paw-punch meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.03,0:24:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch the next episode of\N"March Comes in Like a Lion", too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.70,0:24:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi is fun! Let's all try it together!
